<L>__{interior symington's office day}
<A>__{frances is alone in the room. the door is ajar. she's standing over symington's desk, which is empty except for a doodle pad. the doodle she's looking at is extremely bizarre, sadistic... after a moment, symington enters holding several folders. frances' manner changes very subtly.}
<C>__{symington}
<D>__{...i'm sorry to keep you waiting, the staff review ran over. did you enjoy your mother's visit?}
<C>__{frances}
<P>__{(sitting)}
<D>__{yes. it was very good to see her.}
