<D>__{not at all. she brought me my fan mail.}
<P>__{(a performance)}
<D>__{i had no idea there were so many strangers concerned about me. but i guess that's the best thing about working in the movies. you make so many friends. i want to go back and show them that the faith they put in me wasn't a mistake.}
